>Selected Poems II: Poems Selected and New 1976-1986</TITLE>.</CHRONPROSE><BIBCITS/></CHRONSTRUCT><SHORTPROSE><P><PEDITIONS>This appeared in the <PLACE><GEOG>UK</GEOG></PLACE> as <TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC" REG="Margaret Atwood, Selected Poems, 1976-1986, 1986">Poems 1976-1986</TITLE>, just as her earlier <TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC" REG="Margaret Atwood, Selected Poems 1965-1975, 1976">Selected Poems 1965-1975</TITLE>, 1976, had appeared in the UK with a shorter title.</PEDITIONS> The British publisher in each case was <ORGNAME STANDARD="Virago Press" REG="Virago Press" REF="https://commons.cwrc.ca/orlando:975871be-5061-4ce2-8eb7-631daad9e220">Virago Press</ORGNAME>. A more comprehensive <TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC" REG="Margaret Atwood, Selected Poems 1966-1984, 1990">Selected Poems: 1966-1984</TITLE> followed in 1990, to be joined in 1998 by Virago's yet more comprehensive <TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC" REG="Eating Fire">Eating Fire: Selected Poetry, 1965-95</TITLE>, which incorporated the texts of <TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC" REG="Margaret Atwood, Selected Poems 1965-1975, 1976">Poems 1965-1975</TITLE>, <TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC" REG="Margaret Atwood, Selected Poems 1976-1986, 1986">Poems 1976-1986</TITLE>, and <TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC">Morning in the Burned House</TITLE>. The selected editions of 1986 and 1990 did not appear in the USA.<BIBCITS><BIBCIT PLACEHOLDER="NEOS" DBREF="2742" REF="https://commons.cwrc.ca/orlando:a02f032c-176f-4c9f-9125-4e2c6ccc583b"/><BIBCIT PLACEHOLDER="BLC" DBREF="2052" REF="https://commons.cwrc.ca/orlando:589575c9-c072-42de-b7ac-19398b2b6f2b"/><BIBCIT PLACEHOLDER="CA online" DBREF="16185" REF="https://commons.cwrc.ca/orlando:d0b0dae0-b788-454a-964d-dd2a25ec5dab"/></BIBCITS></P></SHORTPROSE></PRODUCTION></DIV2><DIV2><HEADING><TITLE TITLETYPE="MONOGRAPHIC">Morning in the Burned House</TITLE></HEADING><TEXTSCOPE DBREF="33952" PLACEHOLDER="MA, Morning in the Burned House, 1995" REF="https://commons.cwrc.ca/orlando:b62ac